 overall synchrotron spectrum,\ndiffers significantly from that derived from the X-ray filaments. Finally, the\ntotal mechanical energy released amounts to only $1.8 \\times 10^{50}$ erg,\nuncomfortably low even for a core collapse event.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2007 17:44:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-08-01"}
