 With this statistic, a\nfully ionized universe can be robustly distinguished from one with x_H > 0.5\nusing a survey containing only ~ 20--100 galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2007 20:15:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Jan 2008 22:02:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
